<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="PN356-intro">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. tāyaṅkaṇṇaṉāra.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en">  
      </p>
    </div>  
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PN356">
<l>kaḷari parantu kaḷḷi pōkip</l>
<l>pakaluṅ kūvuṅ kūkaiyoṭu piṟaḻpal</l>
<l>līma viḷakkiṟ pēey makaḷirō</l>
<l>ṭañcuvan taṉṟim mañcupaṭu mutukāṭu</l>
<l>neñcamar kātala raḻuta kaṇṇī</l>
<l>reṉpupaṭu cuṭalai veṇṇī ṟavippa</l>
<l>vellār puṟaṉun tāṉkaṇ ṭulakattu</l>
<l>maṉpataik kellān tāṉāyt</l>
<l>taṉpuṟaṅ kāṇpōrk kāṇpaṟi yātē.</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Fear has come to this old cremation ground engulfed by clouds [of smoke],</l>
<l>with the Pēy women by the lights of the many </l>
<l>irregular pyres, with owls that caw even by day,</l>
<l>Kaḷḷi encroaching, brackish soil spreading.</l>
<l>While tears cried for the lovers dwelling in the heart</l>
<l>extinguish the white ashes on the burning ground littered with bones,</l>
<l>seeing the back of everyone, in the world</l>
<l>it/he being [the same] for all mankind,</l>
<l>it never sees anyone who sees its/his back.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
